50
00:03:20,383 --> 00:03:24,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tadi di sini, 'kan?
Sekali lagi.</font>

51
00:03:32,996 --> 00:03:36,110
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Lalu bagaimana dengan tubuhku?
Dimana tubuhku?</i></font>

52
00:03:38,001 --> 00:03:39,710
