<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi, Bos Preman.</font>

66
00:04:17,574 --> 00:04:19,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau mungkin aku sudah
gila karena kecelakaan itu.</font>

67
00:04:19,809 --> 00:04:21,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, apa dia selalu gila?</font>

68
00:04:21,444 --> 00:04:22,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baik-baik saja?</font>

69
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:25,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa? Kau siapa? Dasar.</font>

70
00:04:36,092 --> 00:04:37,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Wajahmu terlihat baik-baik saja,</font>

71
00:04:37,994 --> 00:04:40,210
