111
00:06:52,295 --> 00:06:53,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda keluarganya?</font>

112
00:06:53,730 --> 00:06:56,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau tahu, aku lebih dekat
dengannya daripada keluarga.</font>

113
00:06:56,599 --> 00:06:59,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku.../ Dia perlu istirahat total.</font>

114
00:06:59,102 --> 00:07:02,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Setiap waktu sangat penting
