120
00:07:16,419 --> 00:07:20,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudku, apa pasien ini akan
terbaring seumur hidup?</font>

121
00:07:25,295 --> 00:07:26,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Cuaca yang cerah.</font>

122
00:07:26,796 --> 00:07:28,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, segarnya.</font>

123
00:07:28,932 --> 00:07:30,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau seharusnya lihat wajah dia.</font>

124
00:07:30,533 --> 00:07:32,430
