00:08:34,097 --> 00:08:35,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Cha Dong Tak.</font>

146
00:08:38,434 --> 00:08:39,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar.</font>

147
00:08:40,803 --> 00:08:43,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus bersikap seperti detektif ini.</font>

148
00:08:43,907 --> 00:08:47,490
