<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

151
00:08:59,923 --> 00:09:02,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian menghabisnya?/
<i>Tidak, makanlah.</i></font>

152
00:09:12,769 --> 00:09:15,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ahjussi. Ahjussi.</i></font>

153
00:09:15,004 --> 00:09:16,220
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hei.</i></font>

154
00:09:16,906 --> 00:09:19,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Ahjussi, kau tidak boleh tidur disini.</font>

155
00:09:19,208 --> 00:09:20,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak mau bangun?</font>

156
00:09:20,410 --> 00:09:22,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selalu tidur
tiap kali berbaring.</font>

157
00:09:22,912 --> 00:09:26,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Tempat tidur ini sangat nyaman./
Ini enak.</font>

158
00:09:28,585 --> 00:09:30,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, aku sangat capek.</font>

159
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:40,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan berbaring.</font>

