175
00:10:30,780 --> 00:10:33,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku libur...</font>

176
00:10:33,082 --> 00:10:36,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Libur? Kembalilah bekerja besok.</font>

177
00:10:36,619 --> 00:10:39,570
